                        "content": "The larger warband is the Attacker, and they use their entire Warband. The smaller warband is the defender, and they can have up to half of the number of models the Attacker has.If both warbands have the same number of models, roll a dice to see who is the attacker and who is the defender.",
                        "subcontent": []
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
